# --- SOLUTION-SPECIFIC IGNORES ---
# Exclude entire projects that are not needed in the final image.
# This is the most effective way to remove test projects.
PropertyDealer.API.Tests/


# --- BUILD ARTIFACTS & CACHES ---
# These are generated inside the container during the 'dotnet build' and
# 'dotnet publish' steps. Excluding them ensures a clean, reproducible build.
**/bin
**/obj
**/node_modules


# --- LOCAL DEVELOPMENT & SECRETS ---
# These files contain settings, secrets, or launch profiles that are
# specific to a developer's machine and should never be in a production image.
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/Properties/launchSettings.json
**/secrets.dev.yaml
**/.env
secrets.json
*.*proj.user
*.suo


# --- IDE / EDITOR CONFIGURATION ---
# These folders contain user-specific settings, state, and cache for IDEs.
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
**/.settings
**/.classpath
**/.project


# --- SOURCE CONTROL ---
# The entire git history is not needed inside the container.
.git/
.gitignore
.gitattributes


# --- DEPLOYMENT & ORCHESTRATION ---
# These files define how to build or deploy the container, but they do
# not belong inside the application image itself.
**/Dockerfile*
.dockerignore
**/docker-compose*
**/charts/
**/values.dev.yaml
**/azds.yaml


# --- DOCUMENTATION & MISCELLANEOUS ---
# General files that add no value to the running application.
README.md
LICENSE
*.md

# OS-generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db